snippet.textDisplay: Great tanks especially i love the Rhino, the name Sickle maybe good, not Hammer, a weak name. Apocalypse tank sadly doesn't scare me, RA2 version is still the best, I like what you did with Union Heavy Tank & the explosion upon its death
